e fraction of useful time based on the relative humidity,\ngust wind speed and presence of clouds. This fraction, ~72%, is very similar to\nthe one derived in Paper I, based on the fraction of time when the extinction\nmonitor is working.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 29 Sep 2008 19:59:30 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-13"}
