 follow the galaxy halo light, suggesting a common\nevolution for these three components. Follow-up spectroscopy can determine\nwhich candidates are truly members of Abell S0740 and how similar they are in\ndistribution to the globulars.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 29 Sep 2008 23:21:51 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-13"}
